Result
The system successfully manages tasks and tracks their progress using a graphical interface and multithreading.

Conclusion
This project demonstrates how Java Swing and multithreading can be used to build an interactive task management system.
It provides practical knowledge of GUI design, event handling, and concurrent programming.
